  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/e90dfee7ce67c20f43a2b9a605e0b6ac.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/e90dfee7ce67c20f43a2b9a605e0b6ac.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Traveler is a rogue-lite action game where you can freely edit skill combo trigger chains. Design your own skill combinations and create different synergies each time; use limited resources to convert and synthesize to get the ideal skill combination, and debug to maximize the effect. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple example of skill chain</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          General attack trigger skill = > skill duration = > trigger the next skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.poster.avif?t=1749351139\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.webm?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.mp4?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a variety of ways to accumulate and charge energy, which makes it convenient for players to edit various skill chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game also has a variety of equipment: mouse range search, automatic search, mobile attack, automatic attack and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely set: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Stereoscopic perspective (perspective perspective)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span>        Flat perspective (parallel perspective) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/e90dfee7ce67c20f43a2b9a605e0b6ac.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/e90dfee7ce67c20f43a2b9a605e0b6ac.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Traveler is a rogue-lite action game where you can freely edit skill combo trigger chains. Design your own skill combinations and create different synergies each time; use limited resources to convert and synthesize to get the ideal skill combination, and debug to maximize the effect. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple example of skill chain</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          General attack trigger skill = > skill duration = > trigger the next skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.poster.avif?t=1749351139\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.webm?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/af0e921a26872b3963d0d56e275b1371.mp4?t=1749351139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a variety of ways to accumulate and charge energy, which makes it convenient for players to edit various skill chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game also has a variety of equipment: mouse range search, automatic search, mobile attack, automatic attack and so on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely set: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Stereoscopic perspective (perspective perspective)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/269ce7f43422dbcd803a72615a53057c.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span>        Flat perspective (parallel perspective) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185720/extras_big/1998231053655de0cb2de1012af004c3.avif?t=1749351139 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
